{"data":{"html":{"path":"/html/config","title":"Project configuration","content":"<h1 id=\"project-configuration\"><a href=\"#project-configuration\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>Project configuration</h1>\n<p>Gridsome requires <code class=\"language-text\">/gridsome.config.js</code> to work. Plugin and project settings are located here. A basic configuration file would look something like this:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\">module<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span>exports <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  siteName<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'Gridsome'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  siteUrl<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'https://www.gridsome.org'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n  plugins<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></pre>\n<h2 id=\"sitename\"><a href=\"#sitename\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>siteName</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Type <code class=\"language-text\">string</code></li>\n<li>Default <code class=\"language-text\">&lt;dirname&gt;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Set a name for your project. The name is typically used in the title tag.</p>\n<h2 id=\"sitedescription\"><a href=\"#sitedescription\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>siteDescription</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Type <code class=\"language-text\">string</code></li>\n<li>Default <code class=\"language-text\">&#39;&#39;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>The description is used as description on your frontpage.</p>\n<h2 id=\"siteurl\"><a href=\"#siteurl\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>siteUrl</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Type <code class=\"language-text\">string</code></li>\n<li>Default <code class=\"language-text\">&#39;&#39;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"pathprefix\"><a href=\"#pathprefix\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>pathPrefix</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Type <code class=\"language-text\">string</code></li>\n<li>Default <code class=\"language-text\">&#39;/&#39;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Gridsome assumes your project is served from the root of your domain.\nChange this option to <code class=\"language-text\">&#39;/my-app&#39;</code> if your project will be hosted in a\nsubdirectory called <code class=\"language-text\">my-app</code>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"titletemplate\"><a href=\"#titletemplate\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>titleTemplate</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Type <code class=\"language-text\">string</code></li>\n<li>Default <code class=\"language-text\">%s - &lt;siteName&gt;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Set a template for the title tag. The <code class=\"language-text\">%s</code> placeholder is replaced with title\nfrom metaInfo you set in your pages.</p>\n<h2 id=\"plugins\"><a href=\"#plugins\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>plugins</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Type <code class=\"language-text\">Array</code></li>\n<li>Default <code class=\"language-text\">[]</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p><a href=\"/docs/install-plugins\">Read more about using plugins</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"icon\"><a href=\"#icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>icon</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Type <code class=\"language-text\">string | Object</code></li>\n<li>Default <code class=\"language-text\">&#39;src/favicon.png&#39;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Gridsome will use any image located at <code class=\"language-text\">src/favicon.png</code> as favicon and\ntouchicon by default, but you can define another path or sizes etc. The icon\nshould be a square and minimum 16 pixels. The favicon will be resized to 16, 32,\n96 pixels. And the touchicon will be resized to 76, 152, 120, 167, 180 pixels by\ndefault.</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  icon<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src/my-icon.png'</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></pre>\n<p>Use a different image for touch icons:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  icon<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    favicon<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src/my-favicon.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    touchicon<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src/my-touchicon.png'</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></pre>\n<p>Define custom sizes and disable effects on iOS &#x3C; 7 devices:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  icon<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    favicon<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      src<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src/my-favicon.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      sizes<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">16</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">32</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">96</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n    touchicon<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      src<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">'src/my-touchicon.png'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      sizes<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">[</span><span class=\"token number\">76</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">152</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">120</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token number\">167</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">]</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      precomposed<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token boolean\">true</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></pre>\n<h2 id=\"chainwebpack\"><a href=\"#chainwebpack\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>chainWebpack</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Type <code class=\"language-text\">Function</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>A function that will receive an instance of ChainableConfig powered by\n<a href=\"https://github.com/neutrinojs/webpack-chain\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">webpack-chain</a>.</p>\n<h2 id=\"configureserver\"><a href=\"#configureserver\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>configureServer</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Type <code class=\"language-text\">Function</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Configure the development server.</p>\n<p><a href=\"/docs/server-api#apiconfigureserverfn\">Read more about configuring the development server</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"cssloaderoptions\"><a href=\"#cssloaderoptions\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>css.loaderOptions</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Type <code class=\"language-text\">Object</code></li>\n<li>Default <code class=\"language-text\">{ sass: { indentedSyntax: true }, stylus: { preferPathResolver: &#39;webpack&#39; } }</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p>Pass options to CSS-related loaders. For example:</p>\n<pre class=\"language-js\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  css<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n    loaderOptions<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n      scss<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// options here will be passed to sass-loader</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>\n      less<span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n        <span class=\"token comment\">// options here will be passed to less-loader</span>\n      <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n    <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span></pre>\n<p>Supported loaders are:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webpack-contrib/css-loader\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">css-loader</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/postcss/postcss-loader\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">postcss-loader</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webpack-contrib/sass-loader\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">sass-loader</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/webpack-contrib/less-loader\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">less-loader</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/shama/stylus-loader\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener noreferrer\">stylus-loader</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"host\"><a href=\"#host\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>host</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Type <code class=\"language-text\">string</code></li>\n<li>Default <code class=\"language-text\">&#39;localhost&#39;</code></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"port\"><a href=\"#port\" aria-hidden=\"true\">#</a>port</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>Type <code class=\"language-text\">number</code></li>\n<li>Default <code class=\"language-text\">8080</code></li>\n</ul>\n","headings":[{"value":"Project configuration"}],"subtitles":[{"value":"siteName","anchor":"#sitename"},{"value":"siteDescription","anchor":"#sitedescription"},{"value":"siteUrl","anchor":"#siteurl"},{"value":"pathPrefix","anchor":"#pathprefix"},{"value":"titleTemplate","anchor":"#titletemplate"},{"value":"plugins","anchor":"#plugins"},{"value":"icon","anchor":"#icon"},{"value":"chainWebpack","anchor":"#chainwebpack"},{"value":"configureServer","anchor":"#configureserver"},{"value":"css.loaderOptions","anchor":"#cssloaderoptions"},{"value":"host","anchor":"#host"},{"value":"port","anchor":"#port"}]}},"context":{}}